Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.26,0:00:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.80,0:00:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫得這麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.19,0:00:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那邊有一家店我很想看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.34,0:00:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為姐姐一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 到底是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.78,0:00:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我約會是這麼地痛苦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.18,0:00:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.22,0:00:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 只是我沒甚麼自信…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.02,0:00:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還擔心著姐姐是否會因對\n這種約會感到厭煩而回去了甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.87,0:00:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.67,0:01:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你剛才說了有一家很想去看看的店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.01,0:01:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個的話 就是那家店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.59,0:01:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.78,0:01:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.16,0:01:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.74,0:01:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.57,0:01:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒緩地行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}貴安、姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.51,0:03:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼千里同學…幹嘛表現得那麼親昵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是半天的約會對象而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來令也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要笑得那麼爽朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空明明是如此地湛藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底都在幹些甚麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的休息日 我也得自己找點開心的事來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生是綠燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著嫉妒的心情駐步不前是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO GO 由乃！ 向前 向前 由乃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有電爐是在預料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大體上仍算一頓美味的午餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.22,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 對我的事你又了解到甚麼程度呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 還看得不夠透徹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.72,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 總有一種甚麼都已被靜大人看穿的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明甚麼都還沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也從未將內心暴露過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間好像還剩不少吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.81,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有今天 忘掉相互的立場與禮儀之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.23,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜大人 為甚麼要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓裙子的下擺亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在走廊下奔跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.68,0:05:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看藏在優等生的面具下的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.86,0:05:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 在情人節那天的白色卡片就如同你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不得不隱藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又同時期望著有人能夠找到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望著被誰理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 擅自闖入了你的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定被你討厭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我喜歡靜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意說出口的話往往接近人的真心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以這樣認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.55,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.43,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼多的褲子裡面 怎樣才能找到自己想要的牛仔褲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得我的信心在一點點地消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐果然是第一次來牛仔褲的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為甚麼對牛仔褲…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我必須要振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請安心 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在你的身邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 這樣我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.02,0:07:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 這裡對面的架子沒有看的必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.55,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為都是男用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣在尋找上花費的功夫一下就減了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.53,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是首條褲子 那就選標準型的藍色牛仔褲如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟祐巳一樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為見到祐巳後才想要牛仔褲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.45,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才才不知不覺地注意上這家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心了真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.21,0:07:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要跟我一樣的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請換好後再叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你量尺寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.25,0:07:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不合你意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.88,0:08:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我失禮一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的腿都好長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了 這個本來就是故意做得很長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.19,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前每次都是截掉這～麼多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.93,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就幫你量尺寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 非常適合你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.09,0:08:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.14,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經想好下一個要去的店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.97,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.65,0:09:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後一場的上映開始時間\n不是前一場上映的結束時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.66,0:09:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說黃薔薇的花蕾\n與田沼千里同學早已出了電影院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 畢竟我也沒注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 抬起頭來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來把目標換到白色上面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指志摩子同學與靜大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩人買了外賣的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在公園或甚麼地方吃午餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 把城裡的公園全找個底朝天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.10,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.06,0:09:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.55,0:09:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果白薔薇大人不在的話 也許我們能成為姐妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.60,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是白薔薇大人現實存在著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都非常喜歡那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們是幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡「Ave Maria」嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 特別是古諾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就讓我發表一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.28,0:10:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包含著今天的感謝之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為東西都還在 所以我想你一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.86,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是被靜叫出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知為何又跟志摩子碰上了面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹甚麼啊 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一旁偷笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.62,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼 只是一想到\N能與姐姐穿一樣的牛仔褲就覺得很高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.26,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我因為穿了這身衣服來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.85,0:14:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在擔心要是跟姐姐不相襯該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.36,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 以前曾一個人很認真地\N想要改正自己與他人不同的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從進入莉莉安的幼兒園開始就一直很拼命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了自己的家用車的接送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.56,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看大部份同班同學所看的電視節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太過拼命竟然還曾臥床不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然會說這些過去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽更多的姐姐過去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 當然也不只是過去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.13,0:14:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 來說說現在的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.87,0:14:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 再稍遠一點的未來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.10,0:14:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來買東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 雖想這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為很在意令與田沼同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.98,0:15:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 心情已經舒暢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妒火中燒而消沉失望 一點都不像我做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 如果不麻煩的話 願意現在跟我們一起去喝茶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不會打擾到你們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.94,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事 就是要熱鬧一點才開心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.05,0:15:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 其實有一家咖啡廳我從以前就一直想去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.49,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人 祐巳同學 還有由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  真是可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔦子同學 照相機怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了這間店後不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.60,0:16:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被店裡的人一句\n「請不要在店內拍照」而封住了我的說詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然打算將花蕾們的約會作為特快消息刊載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天已經將新聞的事全拋開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難得能這麼容易就放棄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這裡的蛋糕真是非常地好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 由乃同學的奶酪蛋糕真不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分我一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶也很香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.15,0:16:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後 三奈子大人完全未提到任何新聞的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔦子同學也一次都未拿出照相機來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.79,0:16:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃也一次都沒說過「令」甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提 我點的巧克力薄紗蛋糕真的是非常地美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.97,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為與祥子大人約會\n的總結的這個預定之外的茶會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.77,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 真是一段非常奢侈而又寶貴的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 又哭又鬧的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你希望的話 我可以陪你到早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.18,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣也許是一種好的趨勢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.87,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子應該更多地\N表現出與年齡相符的弱點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都一個人背負的話會崩潰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.60,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓人看到弱點的話 一定就不會再有誰去責難志摩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.85,0:17:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我再也踏不出一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快春天就要到來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天到了就會有改變嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.71,0:17:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 櫻花盛開 新的邂垢會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與姐姐相遇的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我與志摩子相逢的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.87,0:18:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大人真的是非常地溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 千里同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想來做甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令的家在旁邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.91,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 令大人在無意中 有五次將我叫成了由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.15,0:18:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論說甚麼 去哪裡 令大人的內心裡都有你的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.11,0:18:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個遲鈍的姐姐真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是令的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.65,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是令的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從根本上說 令對女孩子太過溫柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過…太過地溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會稍微地傷害到對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.50,topfont,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 今天真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是小笠原同學的家嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.01,0:19:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉莉安女學園高等部一年級桃組的福澤祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉這麼晚了還打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.18,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否請祥子大人來接聽一下電話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 預先演習完美結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.65,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 先說小笠原「同學」 後又說祥子「大人」會很奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 還是說小笠原大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.83,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想向姐姐打個電話為今天的約會致謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又不知道會由誰來接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.36,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很難打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.20,0:20:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是福澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉這麼晚了還打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉莉安女學園高等部二年級小笠原…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了 是祐巳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.89,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.69,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正想向姐姐家裡打電話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛一打通你就接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.79,0:20:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 今天真是非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.78,0:20:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 向祐巳的家裡打電話真是讓人好緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.19,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直擔心著如果是你的父親或母親接的電話 不知是否能好好地問候他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.85,0:20:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道祐巳是怎樣講述我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是說有一個非常棒的姐姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.66,0:20:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說我是一個既任性又歇斯底裡的姐姐嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說了一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.72,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.65,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.43,0:21:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是開心啊 下次再一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.08,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 是姐姐曾說過的未來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祐巳 晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.91,0:21:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天就能再見到最喜歡的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是如此愉快的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.51,0:21:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天也一定是極好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.83,0:22:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我與姐姐的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.99,0:22:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
